OL,3,CTeachers go on strike over pupil
OL,4,C'violence'
OL,6,FStaff at a school in have walked out
OL,7,Fover claims they are being left
OL,8,F"vulnerable to abuse and violence"
OL,9,Ffrom pupils.
OL,11,FMembers of teaching union the NASUWT
OL,12,Fat Haven High Academy in held their
OL,13,Ffirst of six days of strike action on
OL,14,FWednesday, 17 April, blaming senior
OL,15,Fmanagement for "failing to deal with
OL,16,Fpoor pupil behaviour".
OL,18,FThe union said there was a "lack of
OL,19,Fconsistent sanctions" for students and
OL,20,Fsupport from management.
