OL,6,FAnne Thompson, NASUWT national
OL,7,Fexecutive member for Lincolnshire,
OL,8,Fsaid: "The views and concerns of staff
OL,9,Fhave not been satisfactorily addressed.
OL,11,F"No teacher should go to work
OL,12,Fexpecting to be verbally or physically
OL,13,Fabused and we will continue to take
OL,14,Faction to protect the rights of our
OL,15,Fmembers to a safe working environment
OL,16,Fwhere the learning and progress of
OL,17,Fpupils can be prioritised."
OL,19,F'Requires improvement'
