OL,6,FHaven High was told it required
OL,7,Fimprovement following its last
OL,8,Finspection by the education watchdog
OL,9,Fin November 2022.
OL,11,FOfsted inspectors raised concerns
OL,12,Fabout pupil absences and identified
OL,13,Fsome issues with behaviour.
OL,15,FTheir report said: "Many pupils enjoy
OL,16,Flearning. They are keen to get
OL,17,Finvolved during lessons, and take
OL,18,Fpride in their work.
