OL,6,F"However, the curriculum is not taught
OL,7,Fconsistently well in all subjects and
OL,8,Fyear groups. Some lessons are
OL,9,Fdisrupted by the poor conduct of a few
OL,10,Fpupils. These pupils get distracted
OL,11,Fwhen they struggle with the work and
OL,12,Fdo not get the help they need."
OL,14,FHaven High Academy said it remains
OL,15,F"open to discussing any issues" with
OL,16,Fstaff and the union.
OL,18,FIt added that it wrote to families to
OL,19,Fgive them early notice of the strike
OL,20,Faction, but the union had declined
OL,21,Ffurther talks to limit the disruption.
